==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Heteronym
<hw>Het"er*o*nym</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which is
heteronymous; a thing having a different name or designation from some
other thing; -- opposed to <xex>homonym</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Heteronymous</ent>⟦br⟧
